            "id": 6007336,
            "title": "台泥資產管理事業群啟動首案 擬公開招標出售竹東2872坪土地",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台泥 (1001-TW) 董事會決議，將透過公開招標方式，處分新竹縣竹東鎮的非營業用土地 2872.56 坪，也是台泥資產管理事業群啟動以來，首次落實之策略性資產活化行動，藉此提升資源配置效率。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007336%2Fl%2Fc7e050a27b1372f7a50c38470269acd3.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">台泥資產管理事業群啟動首案 公開招標出售竹東2872坪土地。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台泥表示，這項處分案屬於公司長期資產優化計畫的一環，透過活化部分長期未使用資產，有助於提升營運彈性、強化資產流動性，並支援未來關鍵事業的成長需求。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台泥總經理程耀輝於上周的股東會中透露，目前帳上在台灣大概約有 41 萬坪的非營業用地，可供未來靈活開發與應用。台泥強調，未來將持續依市場變化調整資產配置策略，兼顧營運彈性與資產價值提升。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此外，台泥去年完成對土耳其 OYAK 與葡萄牙 CIMPOR 子公司股權的增持，不僅強化水泥事業的國際低碳布局，也同步擴增了全球土地資產版圖。新增海外土地面積約數百萬坪。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台泥表示，董事會考量整體資產規模快速成長與地域多元化，決議透過策略性出售竹東部分土地，調節地區資源配置，強化全球營運靈活性。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
